commit.message: Adding last version of the DialogFlow agent
Fixed bug when organization parameter is missing. It answered no results, now it works fine
Upload a new backup; README.md updated

Added support for filtering results. Now if you type 'from geogeeks' it filters results from Geo Geeks organization
Upload new backup of dialogflow bot [GISTalkBot_26022018_02_02.zip]
Easier method for dealing with exceptions; Now EXCEPTIONS const values are the literal queries the team provided
Fixed StoryMap buggy use case; now on EXCEPTIONS object we can map words with the proper arcgis type
